         <div xml:id="alalal-ee3790"><!-- l3d2dt1 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-ee3790-Hd1e99">Divisio Textus</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-ee3790-d1e101">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="19"/>DIVISIO TEXTUS.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-ee3790-d1e106">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="20"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-ee3790-Qd1e110">Et quia in homine tota humana 
na<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="21"/>tura, etc. </quote>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="22"/>Hic incipit pars secunda in qua agitur
<lb ed="Bd" n="23"/>de assumpto.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-ee3790-d1e120">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="24"/>Et dividitur in tres partes : in quarum
<lb ed="Bd" n="25"/>prima tangitur quid assumptum est.
<lb ed="Bd" n="26"/>In secunda determinatur, utrum anima
<lb ed="Bd" n="27"/>mediante intellectu, et corpus mediante
<lb ed="Bd" n="28"/>anima assumptum est: et haec 
inci<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="29"/>pit, ibi, B, <quote xml:id="alalal-ee3790-Qd1e135"> Assumpit ergo Dei Filius,
<lb ed="Bd" n="30"/>etc. </quote> In tertia autem determinatur,
<lb ed="Bd" n="31"/>utrum simul tempore assumpsit, et fecit,
<lb ed="Bd" n="32"/>et animam et corpus, ibi, C, <quote xml:id="alalal-ee3790-Qd1e144"> Si 
au<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="33"/>fem quaeritur, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-ee3790-d1e150">
               <cb ed="#Bd" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="34"/>In prima autem parte tria facit. 
Pri<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="35"/>mo probat, quod cum dicitur, <quote xml:id="alalal-ee3790-Qd1e158"> Filius
<lb ed="Bd" n="36"/>assumpsit humanam naturam, </quote> quod
<lb ed="Bd" n="37"/>per naturam humanam intelligitur 
cor<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="38"/>pus et anima. Secundo, inducit errorem
<lb ed="Bd" n="39"/>quorumdam dicentium, quod per 
hu<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="40"/>manam naturam intelligitur proprietas
<lb ed="Bd" n="41"/>sequens corpus et animam conjuncta :
<lb ed="Bd" n="42"/>et destruit per Joannem Damascenum
<lb ed="Bd" n="43"/>qui dicit, quod in Domino Jesu non est
<lb ed="Bd" n="44"/>communem speciem accipere. Tertio,
<lb ed="Bd" n="45"/>inducit Joannem Damascenum dicentem
<lb ed="Bd" n="46"/>eliam, quale assumpsit : quia tale quale
<lb ed="Bd" n="47"/>in nostra natura plantavit.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-ee3790-d1e189">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="48"/>Sententia autem in Littera patebit
<lb ed="Bd" n="49"/>jam per disputationem.
</p>
